---
title: Lemon Pepper Crumbed Haloumi with Wedges, Apple Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: There are plenty of surprises in this delightful meal. With lemon pepper spice blend in the haloumi crumb you get zest,  squeak and crunch, while apple in the slaw gives a sweet contrast. You’ll be wishing you could have this every night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e44b9394a5e5c1e051fe23f-90ba0a6e.jpg
